        ArrayAdapter&lt;String&gt; adapter = new ArrayAdapter&lt;String&gt;(MainActivity.this, android.R.layout.simple_list_item_1,addArray);
        listView.setAdapter(adapter);
    }

And yeah don&#39;t forget to include a `ListView` inside you `activity_saved_password.xml` file.

The **simplest way** to do it is create another class which contains your `ArrayList` which has to be `public static ` like

    public class MyClass {
    
        public static ArrayList&lt;String&gt; addArray;
    }

Then you could add items to your `ArrayList` in your **MainActivity** as

